Title: Get booking by invalid booking ID returns incorrect error response

Description: If user sends a GET request to get a booking by booking ID, using invalid ID. API returns invalid error status code and message

Steps to reproduce:
    1. Send a GET request to get created booking by booking ID using invalid ID (e.g. string value)
    2. Verify response

Expected: 400 status code and some meaningful error message

Actual: 405 "Method Not Allowed" status code and empty response body

Screen recording: https://imgur.com/a/E0wXkdy